<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">驰隙流年，恍如一瞬星霜换，新年的钟声已然响彻四海，时光的诗篇悄然间又翻过一页</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240305/1709649229028053639.jpg" alt="9263eec9e2625fcb9cde893f23804a38.jpg" data-href="" style="width: 158px;height: 241px;"></p><p><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 14px;"><strong>可期未来正舞步蹁跹向我们款款走来</strong></span></p>